======================================================================
PART 1: ORTHOSCHEME DIHEDRAL ANGLES — THE PATTERN
======================================================================

  Orthoscheme Δ_n = {1 ≥ x₁ ≥ x₂ ≥ ... ≥ x_n ≥ 0}

  Facets: F₀ (x₁=1), Fₖ (xₖ=x_{k+1}), F_n (x_n=0)
  Outward normals:
    F₀: e₁
    Fₖ: (-eₖ + e_{k+1})/√2 for k=1,...,n-1
    F_n: -e_n

  n=2:
